creator: Eden Life Inc.
descriptionHtml:
Before we dive into the details, let's take a moment to consider what some customers have had to say about Eden. Feedback from our customers has been overwhelmingly positive, with many praising our high-quality service delivery and robust feature set;

•“Eden Life is the best thing in Nigeria, I’m very picky with food but their food makes me so happy. I’m having ram meat on a normal afternoon and it isn’t even Sallah. Their food is so delicious, I wouldn’t even think of beef on a normal day, but their beef was so delicious 😋 .”•Ronke
•“Started my laundry + cleaning plan with Eden Life today and I’m really excited to never engage with domestic labor ever again.” •Tunde

About Eden

Our goal is to optimize your life with convenient products and services. Let us take care of your chores, so you can save your energy to focus on the things that matter to you. Our services are designed to deliver high-quality experiences and we are always working to improve the value we offer our users.

What can Eden do for you?

•Top Rated Food Options 🍲 •Enjoy a wide variety of gourmet meals, including healthy and chef-cooked options like; Grilled Chicken 🍗 , Peppered Turkey, Beef Assorted 🥩, Stewed Ram Meat 🍖 , Spicy Fried Fish, African Soups 🥘 and Sauces, etc. as well as exclusive choices like brunch 🥞, pastries 🥮 , custom-made lunches, fresh juices 🥤 , and smoothies 🧃. You can order anytime or even get a meal plan on Eden.
•Home Cleaning you can Trust 🧹 •We offer a cleaning service for all your needs, whether it's standard cleaning, deep cleaning, or post-construction cleaning. You can schedule a single service ahead or get a recurring cleaning plan to put your home cleaning on auto-pilot.
•Laundry Pick-Up and Delivery 👔👗•Get your laundry picked up and dropped off within 48 hours, with folding and pressing options available. And like food and cleaning, you can get a dry cleaning plan.
•Self-Care 💅💆‍♂️•Treat yourself to massages, manicures, pedicures, waxing, and threading. All you need to do is schedule your preference on the app.
•Pay for Me 💰•With Eden's "Pay 4 Me" feature, you can get someone to pay for your delicious lunch, brunch, massage, or home makeover. We've made it accessible to everyone with this feature.
•Send Thoughtful Gifts 🎁 •Share the gift of a good life with your friends, colleagues, and loved ones. You can send them a gift card, or even gift them any Eden service of your choice.
•10X Life Tips 📰 •Access information that helps exponentially improve the quality of your life across all our channels.

Why use Eden?

•Relief 😌: Say goodbye to worrying about what to eat next, when to clean, or doing your laundry.
•Comfort 🛌: Get all our services delivered to your doorstep, and subscribers get a personal concierge to help coordinate the delivery of every service.
•Delight and Satisfaction 😁: Enjoy a wide variety of tasty and healthy meals, a home makeover, or a bag of freshly laundered clothes.
•Freedom 🚀: With the shackles of chores gone, you have the freedom to win in life.

- “Eden Life is the best thing in Nigeria, I’m very picky with food but their food makes me so happy. I’m having ram meat on a normal afternoon and it isn’t even Sallah. Their food is so delicious, I wouldn’t even think of beef on a normal day, but their beef was so delicious.”- Ronke
- “Started my laundry + cleaning plan with Eden Life today and I’m really excited to never engage with domestic labor ever again.” - Tunde
About Eden
Our goal is to optimize your life with convenient products and services. What can Eden do for you?
Wide Range of Vetted, Quality Vendors: Get access to a diverse and wide range of vendors with quality products across different categories like food, drinks, supermarkets, health and beauty. You can schedule ahead and distance is not a barrier, we deliver everywhere within Lagos.
Top Rated Food Options, Enjoy a wide variety of gourmet meals, including healthy and chef-cooked options like; Grilled Chicken, Peppered Turkey, Beef Assorted, Stewed Ram Meat, Spicy Fried Fish, African Soups and Sauces, etc. as well as exclusive choices like brunch, pastries, custom-made lunches, fresh juices, and smoothies. You can order anytime or even get a meal plan on Eden.
Home Cleaning You Can Trust. We offer a cleaning service for all your needs, whether it's standard cleaning, deep cleaning, or post-construction cleaning. You can schedule a single service ahead or get a recurring cleaning plan to put your home cleaning on auto-pilot.
Laundry Pick-Up and Delivery. Get your laundry picked up and dropped off within 48 hours, with folding and pressing options available. And like food and cleaning, you can get a dry cleaning plan.
Self-Care. Treat yourself to massages, manicures, pedicures, waxing, and threading. All you need to do is schedule your preference on the app.
Pay for Me. With Eden's Pay 4 Me feature, you can get someone to pay for your delicious lunch, brunch, massage, or home makeover. We've made it accessible to everyone with this feature.
